The "Documentation" directory serves as the knowledge hub for the ConsciousTechHub repository. It includes essential information for contributors, developers and users.

Project Guidelines : A comprehensive guide outlining the principles and guidelines for contributing to ConciousTechHub projects.Covers coding standards, ethical coding practices and guidelines for maintaing a conscious tech development environment. Encourages contributors to align their work with the conscious tech vision.

User Guides : Guides for end-users on how to interect with and make the most of conscious tech solutions developed within the hub. Provides clear instructions on installation, usage and any ethical considerations for users.

API Reference : Detailed documentation on APIs used in conscious tech projects. Ensures clarity for developers working on integrating or extending existing solutions within the hub.
